{"id": "pos002", "name": "Cam_Noah_693_03_16", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Cherry's_Door", "Door opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "I'm home.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Just in time. I am making coffee.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Hmm, add a bit more sugar today.\nWhere's Aroma?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "She's taking a bath... Hmm? Looks like she's just got done with that.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Ah, Noah... sorry. You can use the bathroom now.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos0201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<i>*Chuckles*</i> You don't have to be so cautious. We are living together after all. Just treat me like family.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Ok... thank you for letting me live together with you guys. It feels like I'm disturbing you two newlyweds though...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "No need to worry. Having you together with us makes Helena happier too. If I were the only one here, she would probably give me a long face every day. That would be quite the waste of that beautiful face, don't you think?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Stop your flattering, it's gross...\nAroma, do you want some coffee?\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Ah, I'll pour it myself...\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "No. You must be exhausted after a whole day at the studio, aren't you? You get some rest; I'll do it.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Congratulations on second place. You were great!\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Tuner-san]"], "content": "<i>Congrats! Congrats</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "... Don't be disheartened. Compare to the first-place winner, your performance created even more buzz on iM.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Eh?\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "See for yourself...\n[No.12 is so cuuuute!! Her voice is amazing too!]\n[Ten times better than the actual winner, stupid organizer and their shady BS]\n[I'm in love. Can someone get me her iM account]...\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "S, stop reading them out loud! It's embarrassing... Also, the first-place winner is much better than me...\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "I saw the live stream. If we were to judge only by singing, then you are indeed the winner.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aren't you at work?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "The research department is not really busy these days due to that previous incident... Ah, right; the camera also caught you tearing up. How rare, seeing as you seem to have a poker face 24/7.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "... I, I did not!?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "If you don't believe, check the clip. It's been spreading like wildfire online already.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward »»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "... Another listen and it's still as amazing as the first time. You indeed have the best singing performance.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "You guys are exaggerating...\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Aroma, have some confidence in yourself. With that singing voice of yours, your dream of being a world-class singer will come true one day. I guarantee it.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "... Ok.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Even you are saying that... I will try my best, thank you. Feels like Noah is really good at comforting people. Your words calm people down... makes me a little jealous of sister, hehe.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "You're thinking too much. What good does this guy have?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "What's wrong?\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "... Hmm? Ah, nothing. Is the coffee done?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Should be almost done. I'll go check it out.\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Let me do it.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "You two tired folks should stop trying to take my job. Sit down.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "No, you were even more nervous than Aroma last night. You barely got any sleep, did you? I'll do...\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"3.2\">I SAID, SIT, DOWN.</font>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Tuner-san]"], "content": "<i>Detects Anger Emotion</i>\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<font size=\"2.0\">In times like this, it's best you listen to sister...</font>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"2.0\">Haha... seems like that's the case.</font>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Cherry's_Door", "ドアが開く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "ただいま。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "あら、おかえりなさい。\nちょうどよかった。\n今コーヒー淹れてるの。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "あぁ、今日は砂糖大目で頼むよ。\nAromaちゃんは？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "今お風呂に……あら？あがったみたいね。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "あ、Noahさん……ごめんなさい。\nお風呂どうぞ。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos0201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "ハハ！そんなにかしこまらなくていいよ。\n一緒に住んでるんだから、僕のことも家族だと思って、ね？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "はい……あの、家に置いてくれて、2人ともありがとう。\n新婚夫婦のジャマをしちゃって……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "気にしないで。\n君がいると、Helenaも喜ぶんだ。\n僕だけじゃ、いつもブスッとして、楽しそうな顔なんて見せてくれないよ。\nきれいな顔なのにもったいないと思わない？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "ちょっと、いい加減なこと言わないで……\nAroma、あなたもコーヒー飲む？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "あ、私自分でやる……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "ダメよ。\nまる一日撮影で疲れたでしょう？\n休んでなさい。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "2位だったんだってね。おめでとう。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[チューナー君]"], "content": "<i>オメデトウ！オメデトウ！</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……そんなに落ち込まないで。\n1位の子より、君の方がiMで話題になってるよ。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "え？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "ほら……\n「12番かわいすぎない！？歌声も超いい」\n「1位より2位の方がうまかったのに。出来レースじゃん」\n「惚れた。だれかこの子のiM探してください」\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "よ…読まないで！恥ずかしい……\n1位の子の方がすごかったもん……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "生放送を見てたけど、君の歌声は間違いなく1番だったよ。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "仕事はどうしたの？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "ほら、あのことがあってから、研究部はヒマなんだ……\nそういえば、君が涙を浮かべてる様子が映ってたよ。\nポーカーファイスの君が珍しいね\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "…っな！？私がまさか！！\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "信じられないなら、動画見てみなよ。\nネット上でたくさん上がってるから。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "何回聞いても素晴らしいわ。\nやっぱりあなたが1番よ。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "それは言い過ぎだよ……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Aromaちゃん、自分に自信を持つんだ。\n君の実力なら、夢は必ずかなう。\n世界的な歌手になれる。\n僕が保証するよ。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……うん。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noahさんがそこまで言うなら……私、がんばるね。\nありがとう。\nNoahさん、人を慰めるのが上手だよね。\nなんか安心するって言うか……\nお姉ちゃんにヤキモチ焼いちゃうなぁ～へへ\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "そんなことないわよ。\nこの人のどこがいいの？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "どうしたの？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……ん？いや、なんでもないよ。\nコーヒーは？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "そろそろだと思うわ。\n見てくる。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "いや、僕がやるよ。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "ちょっと、1日働いてきた2人が私の仕事を取らないでよ。\n座って。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "いや、君は昨日Aromaちゃんより緊張してただろう？\nほとんど寝てないんじゃないか？やっぱり僕が……\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"3.2\">い い か ら 座 っ て て 。</font>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[チューナー君]"], "content": "<i>怒リヲ検測シマシタ</i>\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<font size=\"2.0\">こういう時は、大人しく言うこと聞いた方がいいよ……</font>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"2.0\">ハハ……そうみたいだね。</font>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Cherry's_Door", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我回來了。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "正好，我剛好在煮咖啡。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "嗯，今天多加一點糖。\nAroma 呢？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "在洗澡……嗯？好像洗好了。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "啊，Noah……抱歉，浴室可以用了。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos0201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "呵呵，不用那麼拘謹啦。\n都住在一起了，就當一家人就好。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……謝謝你讓我和你們一起住，總覺得會打擾到你們新婚夫妻……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "不會不會，有妳一起 Helena 也比較開心。只有我的話她大概會每天擺張臭臉，不就可惜了這麼漂亮的臉蛋？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "你少來了，阿諛諂媚的……\nAroma 要不要喝咖啡？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "啊，我自己來……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "不行，錄影一整天很累吧？妳休息，我來。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "恭喜妳拿了第二名，很厲害呢。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>恭喜！恭喜！</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……別喪氣了。比起第一名，妳的表現在 iM 的討論度更高喔。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "咦？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "妳看……\n「12號太正了吧！？歌聲也超美」\n「比第一名強十倍，主辦黑箱太超過了」\n「戀愛了，求神人提供 iM 帳號」……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "別、別唸了啦！好害羞……而且第一名比我厲害很多……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我看了直播，光論歌聲，妳確實是第一名喔。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "你不是在上班？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "因為之前那件事所以現在研究部門很閒……對了，鏡頭有照到妳眼角泛淚。真難得，明明平常一張撲克臉。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……我、我哪有！？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "不信我開影片，現在網路已經在瘋傳了喔。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……再聽一次還是覺得好棒，果然妳唱得才是最好的。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "太誇張了啦……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Aroma，要對自己有信心，以妳的歌聲總有一天會達成夢想，成為世界級的歌星，我保證。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……嗯。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "連你都這麼說了……我會加油的，謝謝你。總覺得 Noah 好會安慰人喔，讓人感覺很安心……有點忌妒姊姊了，嘿嘿。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "妳想太多了，這種傢伙哪裡好了？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "怎麼了？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……嗯？啊，沒事啊。咖啡好了沒？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "應該快好了，我去看看。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我來好了。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "兩個累了一整天的人別一直想搶我的工作，坐好。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "不，妳昨天晚上比 Aroma 還緊張，幾乎沒睡吧？還是我……\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"3.2\">我．說．坐．好。</font>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>偵測到憤怒情緒</i>\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<font size=\"2.0\">這種時候還是聽姊姊的比較好喔……</font>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"2.0\">哈哈……好像是。</font>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Cherry's_Door", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "나 왔어.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "마침 딱 도착했네.\n지금 막 커피 끓이고 있었는데.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "응. 설탕 좀 많이 넣어줘.\nAroma는?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "씻고 있어……응? 지금 다 씻은 것 같은데.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "아, Noah 씨…… 죄송해요.\n지금 막 끝났어요.... 욕실 사용하셔도 되요....\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos0201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "하하. 너무 그렇게 어려워할 필요 없단다. 여기서 함께 살고 있으니 가족이나 마찬가지라고. 너무 어색해 하지 마렴.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "네……이곳에서 지낼 수 있게 해주셔서 감사해요. 이제 막 신혼인 두 분께 이렇게 폐만 끼치고...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "그렇게 생각할 필요 없단다.\n네가 있어야 Helena도 더 기뻐할 테니깐.\n만약 나 혼자만 있었다면 맨날 찡그리는 표정만 짓고 있을 테니깐. 그렇게 이쁜 얼굴로 아깝게 말이야.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "제발 좀! 아부 좀 그만 떠시죠?\nAroma, 커피 마실래?\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "아, 내가 직접 따를 게...\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "안돼.\n오늘 하루 종일 녹화 때문에 피곤 하잖아?\n좀 쉬어야지. 내가 할테니, 자.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "2등했다면서. 정말 축하한다. \n역시 대단하구나.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[튜너 군]"], "content": "<i>축하! 축하!</i>\n\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……너무 낙심하지 마렴.\niM에서는 1등한 그 사람보다 네 공연 얘기를 훨씬 더 많이 하고 있다고.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "네?\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "이것 봐봐……\n「12번 참가자 짱 이쁘다! 목소리도 완전 꿀보이스」\n「1등보다 10배 잘했는데 어이 상실. 100% 돈 먹었겠지?」\n「입덕해버림. 혹시 저 사람 iM 계정 아시는 분」……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "읽, 읽지 마세요! 부끄럽잖아요....\n그리고 1등한 사람은 저보다 훨씬 뛰어난……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "방송 봤는데, 노래로 따지고 보면 무조건 네가 1등이었어.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "출근 안해도 돼?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "예전에 그 일 때문에 지금 연구부는 매우 한가롭다고..... 아참, 카메라에 당신 눈물 글썽이는 모습 잡혔던데. 참 희한해. 항상 포커페이스인 당신이 말이야.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……내가? 설마!\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "못 믿겠으면 영상 봐봐. 인터넷에 이미 다 돌아다니고 있다고.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……다시 들어도 역시 네 노래가 1등을 했어야 해.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "말도 안돼... 너무 그러지 마……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Aroma. 네 스스로에게 자신을 좀 가져보렴. 네 실력은 충분히 세계적인 가수가 될 수 있는 레벨이야. 내가 보증하지.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……네.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noah 씨도 그렇게 말씀하시니.... 저 더 힘내볼게요. 고마워요. Noah씨는 정말 사람을 잘 위로해주는 것 같아요.... 언니한테 조금은 질투가 나는 데? 헤헤...\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "무슨 말도 안되는 소리야.\n이런 사람이 어디가 좋다고.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "왜 그러세요?\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……응? 아, 아니야 아무것도. \n커피는?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "거의 다 된 것 같아.\n가서 보고 올게.\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "아니, 그냥 내가 할게.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "두 사람 다 하루 종일 피곤했잖아.\n자꾸 내 할 일까지 전부 가로채지 말라고.\n그냥 앉아있어.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "아니. 당신 어제 Aroma보다 더 긴장해있었잖아. 잠도 거의 못 잤지? 그러니깐 내가....\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"3.2\">앉．아．있．으 . 라 . 니 . 깐. 좀 .</font>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[튜너 군]"], "content": "<i>분노 감정이 감지 됨</i>\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<font size=\"2.0\">이럴 땐 그냥 언니 말 따르는 게 안전할 거에요……</font>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"2.0\">하하…… 그래야 할 것 같구나.</font>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Cherry's_Door", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我回來了。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "正好，我剛好在煮咖啡。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "嗯，今天多加一點糖。\nAroma 呢？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "在洗澡……嗯？好像洗好了。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "啊，Noah……抱歉，浴室可以用了。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos0201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "呵呵，不用那麼拘謹啦。\n都住在一起了，就當一家人就好。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……謝謝你讓我和你們一起住，總覺得會打擾到你們新婚夫妻……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "不會不會，有妳一起 Helena 也比較開心。只有我的話她大概會每天擺張臭臉，不就可惜了這麼漂亮的臉蛋？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "你少來了，阿諛諂媚的……\nAroma 要不要喝咖啡？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "啊，我自己來……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "不行，錄影一整天很累吧？妳休息，我來。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "恭喜妳拿了第二名，很厲害呢。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>恭喜！恭喜！</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……別喪氣了。比起第一名，妳的表現在 iM 的討論度更高喔。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "咦？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "妳看……\n「12號太正了吧！？歌聲也超美」\n「比第一名強十倍，主辦黑箱太超過了」\n「戀愛了，求神人提供 iM 帳號」……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "別、別唸了啦！好害羞……而且第一名比我厲害很多……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我看了直播，光論歌聲，妳確實是第一名喔。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "你不是在上班？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "因為之前那件事所以現在研究部門很閒……對了，鏡頭有照到妳眼角泛淚。真難得，明明平常一張撲克臉。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……我、我哪有！？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "不信我開影片，現在網路已經在瘋傳了喔。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……再聽一次還是覺得好棒，果然妳唱得才是最好的。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["