na"], "content": "……再听一次还是觉得好棒，果然妳唱得才是最好的。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "太夸张了啦……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Aroma，要对自己有信心，以妳的歌声总有一天会达成梦想，成为世界级的歌星，我保证。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……嗯。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "连你都这么说了……我会加油的，谢谢你。总觉得 Noah 好会安慰人喔，让人感觉很安心……有点忌妒姊姊了，嘿嘿。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "妳想太多了，这种家伙哪里好了？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "怎么了？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……嗯？啊，没事啊。咖啡好了没？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "应该快好了，我去看看。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我来好了。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "两个累了一整天的人别一直想抢我的工作，坐好。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "不，妳昨天晚上比 Aroma 还紧张，几乎没睡吧？还是我……\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"3.2\">我．说．坐．好。 </font>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>侦测到愤怒情绪</i>\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<font size=\"2.0\">这种时候还是听姊姊的比较好喔……</font>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"2.0\">哈哈……好像是。 </font>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}